Text:
The Lady Killer is the third solo studio album by recording artist Cee Lo Green. 
It's set to be released on November 9, 2010, by Elektra Records, Roadrunner Records. 
The album's lead single "Fuck You!", was released on August 19, 2010, and placed #17 
on the Billboard Hot 100. The album is available to stream at NPR until November 9, 2010...
